 Details Hidden


Guggenheim Partners Investment Management LLC

                                    Guggenheim Investments is the investment management business of Guggenheim Partners. We have a long, distinguished history of serving institutional investors, ultra-high-net-worth individuals, family offices and financial intermediaries. We offer clients a wide range of differentiated capabilities built on a proven commitment to investment excellence.

Our business is firmly rooted in the discipline of institutional money management; our DNA is etched with the rigor of managing risk. Each of our investment teams brings a unique expertise and point of view about what drives asset and market behavior and what drives risk and reward. Each of our teams adheres to a strict risk discipline, minding both sides of the risk-reward equation.

Over the years, clients have valued our independence, thought leadership, innovation and a nimbleness not readily found in other major players in the industry. As a privately-owned firm, we are answerable only to our clients and to our commitment to their success.                                




