SandRidge Energy Inc:Tumbling oil prices continued to shake the local economy Wednesday as SandRidge Energy Inc. laid off 172 Oklahoma City employees - the Oklahoman.The company has cut 440 jobs since the first of the year - the Oklahoman. 
			
